remarks: Commutative law for double substitution into a class.  (Contributed by NM, 14-Nov-2005.)  Obsolete as of 18-Aug-2018.  Use ~ csbcom instead. (New usage is discouraged.)  (Proof modification is discouraged.)
statement:
csbcomgOLD $p |- ( ( A e. V /\ B e. W ) -> [_ A / x ]_ [_ B / y ]_ C = [_ B / y ]_ [_ A / x ]_ C ) $.
$d A y $.
$d B x $.
